\nserved with chickpea mash  34\n\n<strong>CENTER-CUT SIRLOIN SHASHLIK</strong>fire-roasted tender slices of marinated beef,\nbell peppers and sweet onions  31\n\n<strong>FIRE-ROASTED CHICKEN SHASHLIK</strong>eastern mediterranean spices, italian parsley and garden tomatoes, oregano fries  25\n\n<strong>GRILLED HANGER STEAK FRITES</strong> hand cut oregano fries and barrel aged balsamic,\nolive and tomato relish 25\n\n<strong>FIRE-ROASTED CHICKEN SHASHLIK</strong> marinated breast, bell peppers, sweet onions\nand extra virgin olive oil  25\n\n<strong>ROASTED AUBERGINE WITH SWEET CHILI TOMATO SAUCE</strong> seasonal market vegetables,\nfresh herbs  19[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h2>SIGNATURE COCKTAILS 14</h2>\n<strong>PERA RICKEY</strong> bacardi white  sour cherry nectar  rosemary syrup  lime  soda\n\n<strong>BLACK MANHATTAN</strong> makers mark  averna  orange bitters\n\n<strong>NEW FASHIONED</strong> knob creek  amaretto  bitters  orange peel\n\n<strong>TURKISH APRICOT MARGARITA</strong> don julio blanco  apricot puree  triple sec\n\n<strong>BLOOD ORANGE MARTINI</strong> zyr  don benedictine  blood orange puree  orange bitters  lemon\n\n<strong>THE CORDOVAR</strong> bulldog  prosecco  agave  lemon twist\n\n<strong>SPICY MANGO GIMLET</strong> bombay sapphire  mango puree[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h2>SPARKLING WINES</h2>\n<strong>JACQUES PELVAS </strong> blanc de blancs brut, france  12\n\n<strong>CUPCAKE VINEYARDS </strong> prosecco, veneto - italy  13[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h2>ROSE WINE</h2>\n<strong>2011 PAUL JABOULET PARALLEL 45 </strong> st. tropez  12[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h2>RED WINES</h2>\n<strong>2011 DOMAINE BRUNET</strong> pinot noir, pays doc  12\n\n<strong>2012 RENACER PUNTO FINAL</strong> malbec, argentina  12\n\n<strong>2010 ZENATO</strong> valpolicella superiore, italy  13\n\n<strong>2009 PENA REJAS CRIANZA </strong> tempranillo, spain  14\n\n<strong>2011 EGEO </strong> cabernet sauvignon, turkey  15\n\n<stron