>ROASTED BRUSSELS SPROUT</strong> w/ pistachios &amp; kasseri cheese  8[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h2>WHITE WINES</h2>\n<strong>2012 FORNAS</strong> pinot grigio, delle venezie, italy  11\n\n<strong>2012 ANDERRA BY ROTHSCHILD</strong> sauv. blanc, chile  12\n\n<strong>2012 ARGYROS ATLANTIS</strong> assyrtiko, santorini-greece  12\n\n<strong>2011 GRAYSON CELLARS </strong> chardonnay, california  13\n\n<strong>2010 LARIELLA </strong> greco di tufo docg, italy  13\n\n<strong>2010 MOUNTFORD </strong> riesling, new zealand  14[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}s:26:\"hours-direction_2069498562\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:15:\"Hours Direction\";s:8:\"template\";s:2600:\"[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"hours-direction\"][vc_text_separator title=\"Hours\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\"][vc_row_inner el_class=\"spacing-bottom\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Sunday - Thursday</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>12:00pm - 10:30pm</em></p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Friday - Saturday</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>12:00pm - 11:30pm</em></p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>*kitchen closes 30 minutes prior to published closing times</em></p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Directions\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"no-spacing\"]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">54 Thompson Street, New York, NY 10012 at the corner of Broome Street</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Subway</strong></p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"blue\">E</span> to Spring Street\n<span class=\"red\">1</span> to Canal Street\n<span class=\"yellow\">N</span> <span class=\"yellow\">Q</span> to Canal Street[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Parking</strong></p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]<em>Closest garage is on West Broadway between Broome and Grand Streets (1 block away). Other nearby garages are located on West Broadway between Grand and Canal Streets (2 blocks) and on the corner of Grand Street and Wooster Street (2.5 blocks).</em>\n\n<em>Street parking may be hard to come by in Soho (especially on weekends), the best bets would be on Grand Street, on 6th Avenue and on West Broadway</em>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"hours-img\"][vc_gmaps type=\"m\" zoom=\"14\" link=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3023.7339412256215!2d-74.0034359!3d40.72387314999999!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c2598c80b90e3d%3A0x8c053fe36e7d8561!2sPera+Soho!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1391704080527\" size=\"875\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}}", "yes");
