INSERT INTO `wp_2_posts` VALUES("271", "2", "2014-02-07 01:01:27", "2014-02-07 01:01:27", "[vc_row el_class=\"slider-wrapper\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\" el_class=\"slider-container\"][vc_column_text][new_royalslider id=\"1\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" el_class=\"slider-ads\"][vc_column_text][adrotate banner=\"8\"]\n[adrotate banner=\"8\"]\n[adrotate banner=\"8\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text][post_listing post_type=\"event\" title=\"Latest Events\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text][post_listing title=\"From The Blog\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"home-blocks\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>BEYOND THE ORDINARY</h3>\nOur signature mezes and entree dishes that are so popular with New Yorkers made the trip with us when we opened another Pera in Soho. But we took our customers off the beaten path into parts of Eastern Mediterranean cuisine that rarely make it across the Atlantic. Like only the best restaurants in New York, we challenge your taste buds with incredible creations, such as Pistachio Crusted Snapper and Marinated Sliced Sirloin Steak Shaslik.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>DECOR</h3>\nThe interior of Pera Soho is one of inviting sophistication, fitting perfectly into the community. A rich palette of colors capture the unique aesthetic of Soho, a neighborhood full of art galleries, historical architecture and designer boutiques that makes it like no other area of New York. With large windows, the bar has a bright and airy feel, while the main dining room is both intimate and comfortable.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>FINE DINING SOHO-STYLE</h3>\nSoho is a neighborhood that has gone through a rebirth, and the best restaurants in Soho reflect this resurgence. Pera Soho has that same energy joining the vibrancy of Mediterranean cuisine with the trendiness that is on every street in Soho. Similarly, Pera Soho serves Mediterranean food that offers you both the classic dishes while taking lamb, steak, chicken and fish to exciting new places.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]", "Home", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "41-autosave-v1", "", "", "2014-02-07 01:01:27", "2014-02-07 01:01:27", "", "41", "http://soho.pera.wpengine.com/2014/02/06/41-autosave-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
