INSERT INTO `wp_3_posts` VALUES("41", "3", "2014-01-27 20:01:26", "2014-01-27 20:01:26", "[vc_row el_class=\"slider-wrapper\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\" el_class=\"slider-container\"][vc_column_text][new_royalslider id=\"1\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" el_class=\"slider-ads\"][vc_column_text][adrotate group=\"1\"]\r\n[adrotate group=\"3\"]\r\n[adrotate group=\"2\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text][post_listing post_type=\"event\" title=\"Latest Events\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text][post_listing title=\"From The Blog\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"home-blocks\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>YOUR 42ND STREET NEIGHBOR</h3>\r\nThe awe one feels for Grand Central Station never grows old. Every day, history collides with urbanites, commuters and tourists as they brush up against this NYC marvel. Just around the corner, Pera invites you to feast on the best NYC restaurant fare, with the care and attention you would expect from a restaurant near Grand Central..[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>EXQUISITE CUISINE</h3>\r\nMidtown is the best NYC restaurant when it comes to balancing a unique cuisine with New York style. Pera is like no other restaurant near Grand Central, and nothing delights the taste buds like Peras mezes. Some savory, some spicy, Pera mezes will introduce you to a new world of flavors.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>FLAWLESS SERVICE</h3>\r\nPera goes the extra mile to give you the best NYC restaurant experience. Like our beautiful dcor, our service befits your idea of exceptional fine dining. From the moment you enter our restaurant near Grand Central, we see to it, by being discreet, professional and courteous, that upon leaving you feel that your standards have been surpassed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]", "Home", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "home", "", "", "2014-03-21 18:36:22", "2014-03-21 18:36:22", "", "0", "http://pera.gmclients.wpengine.com/?page_id=41", "0", "page", "", "0");
