INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("471", "2", "2013-06-19 09:00:29", "2013-06-19 09:00:29", "<i>Hey Boo Boo, lets go get us a pic-a-nic basket!</i>\n\nYogi Bear, the famous cartoon character, was obsessed with picnic baskets.\n\nToday, people still find joy in a simple summer picnic in the park.\n\nYogi must have been on to something\n<h3><b>Summer Picnics In the Park</b></h3>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/12247055@N00/1508168478\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"zemanta-img-inserted zemanta-img-configured alignright\" title=\"picnic basket\" alt=\"picnic basket\" src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2059/1508168478_0b43844910_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"180\" /></a>\n\nMany of us have great summer memories.\n\nIt might be riding your first bike, hanging out at the pool or\n\nmaybe having a summer picnic with family and friends.\n\nFor others, the memory might be an<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 10px;line-height: 17px\">)</span>evening picnic with someone special. You spread the blanket out on the soft grass. You unpack a few tasty treats and maybe a bottle of wine with two glasses.\n\nIts a great setting for creating a special memory.\n\nSomething every summer picnic need is a great picnic basket.\n\nWhether you get a ready-to-go basket from a favorite restaurant or put together your own, your picnic will be even better with a basket.\n\nYogi <i>was</i> on to something.\n<h3><b>Picnic Baskets Delivered To Your Door</b></h3>\nThere are a few options for getting a picnic basket together.\n\nFirst, you can have a complete basket and meal created for you. One of a few services will sell all non-perishables and can ship a complete basket to you.\n\nBaskets include smoked meats, crackers, nuts, dried fruits, and drinks.\n<h3><b>Fresh Picnic Baskets From Your Favorite Restaurant</b></h3>\nA second option is to go straight to your favorite restaurant.\n\nYou can order gourmet baskets with fresh and exotic foods.\n\nClassier than a Styrofoam takeout box, restaurants are offering adorable baskets filled with delicious dishes that can be shared among a group of friends, or on a romantic outing for two.\n\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/51035735481@N01/8216461706\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"zemanta-img-inserted zemanta-img-configured alignleft\" title=\"Picnic basket\" alt=\"Picnic basket\" src=\"http://farm9.static.flickr.com/8489/8216461706_3b3a3cb067_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"160\" /></a>\n\nRestaurants usually make it easy and include napkins and flatware as well. All you need to tell them is the number of people and they will have an amazing picnic ready for you in record time.\n<h3></h3>\n<h3><b>Creating Your Own Picnic Basket</b></h3>\nThe third option is to create your own basket.\n\nWhen putting together your own picnic basket, ensure you pack the right amount of food for the number of people youre feeding.\n\nTheres no need to bring massive amounts of sandwiches, salad, fruit, chips, and dessert if there will just be two of you.\n\nFor picnics, flavor is more important than quantity.\n\nFind the most flavorful options and add snacking portions instead of full portions. Youll find that sampling delicious snacks will fill you up.\n<h3><b>Additional Picnic Basket Items</b></h3>\nWe recommend including a lightweight activity in your picnic basket.\n\nA deck of cards or a nice book to read in the park would be a good addition.\n\nMaking an event out of your picnic instead of just a meal will make it even more special.\n\nWhether youre taking the kids for a picnic or taking a date, an activity will keep everyone entertained as you enjoy the great summertime weather.\n<h3><b>Perfect Picnic Spots</b></h3>\nFinding the perfect spot is the start to a great picnic.\n\nFind somewhere that wont be awkward to be seated on the ground and will be out of the way of pedestrians. Flat, grassy and out of the way is the ideal location for a picnic.\n\nOn a hot day, park yourself under the shade of a big tree and enjoy staying cool. Bring along a blanket to sit on to make you and your guests more comfortable. The blanket will also help keep any mischievous bugs away from your food.\n\n<a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Pinic_table_at_Hamby_Park_-_Hillsboro%2C_Oregon.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"zemanta-img-inserted zemanta-img-configured alignright\" title=\"Swings and picnic table at U. J. Hamby Park in...\" alt=\"Swings and picnic table at U. J. Hamby Park in...\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ee/Pinic_table_at_Hamby_Park_-_Hillsboro%2C_Oregon.JPG/300px-Pinic_table_at_Hamby_Park_-_Hillsboro%2C_Oregon.JPG\" width=\"230\" height=\"169\" /></a>\n\nYou can always set up at a picnic table if they are offered in the park you find. This gives you a stable surface to set out food and youll be sure you arent in anyones way.\n<h3><b>Sunset Picnics</b></h3>\nIf summer days are just too hot to be outside for long periods of time where you are, think about a sunset or moonlight picnic.\n\nAdd candles - maybe citronella to deter bugs - to your picnic basket essentials and think about bringing a bottle of wine.\n\nThe perfect romantic summer date, a nighttime picnic is sure to impress your significant other.\n\nIf your favorite local park doesnt allow open containers of alcohol you could always sneak back to your own place to extend the picnic fun.\n\nDont forget the corkscrew and we suggest plastic wine glasses just in case.\n\nSummer is here.\n\nGet outside and enjoy the summer weather with a picnic this year.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nCheck out Pera Events and Catering for their great selection of <a href=\"http://peranyc.com/pera_picnic_baskets.html\">picnic baskets</a>.\n\n<b>Enjoy your pic-a-nic basket, Boo-Boo!</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class=\"zemanta-pixie\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;height: 15px\"><a class=\"zemanta-pixie-a\" title=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" href=\"http://www.zemanta.com/?px\"><img class=\"zemanta-pixie-img\" style=\"border: none;float: right\" alt=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" src=\"http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=407a7520-defc-455f-aa54-d149d031d160\" /></a></div>", "The Perfect Picnic Basket ", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "the-perfect-picnic-basket", "", "", "2013-06-19 09:00:29", "2013-06-19 09:00:29", "", "0", "http://peranyc.com/blog/?p=471", "0", "post", "", "0");
