ed wine vinaigrette  13</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;\">add crumbled sheep\'s milk feta cheese to any of the above salads  13</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title=\"Dinner Menu\" tab_id=\"1395899620491-1-7\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>5:00PM - 9:00PM</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Appetizers</h2>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>(please select one)</em></h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>AVGOLEMONO SOUP</strong> greek-style chicken, lemon &amp; egg soup</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>MEDITERRANEAN ANGEL EGGS</strong> deviled eggs with spicy hummus</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>TURKISH ZUCCHINI PANCAKES</strong> smoked salmon and garlic labne</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PERA EASTER SALAD</strong> wild arugula, tomatoes, onions, fried chickpeas, purpled egg</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Main Courses</h2>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>(please select one)</em></h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>MUSTARD HERB CRUSTED HAM</strong> chili glazed carrots, dirty potatoes</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>INSIDE OUT LAMB PERSILLADE</strong> couscous with dried apricots and pine nuts</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PAN SEARED MEDITERRANEAN DORADE</strong> mixed vegetable and quinoa tabouleh</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>SPRING VEGETABLE BUCATINI</strong> hollow tube pasta with sundried tomatoes, asparagus and garlic butter sauce</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Dessert</h2>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>(please select one)</em></h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>GOATS MILK CHEESE CAKE</strong> roasted fig syrup</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PORTOKALOPITA</strong> warm orange cake</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CHOCOLATE CARDAMOM MOUSSE</strong> sweet turkish cream cheese</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>$29</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>(not including tax and gratuity)</em></h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][/vc_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]", "Happy Easter", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "happy-easter-2014", "", "", "2014-03-29 21:07:49", "2014-03-29 21:07:49", "", "0", "http://pera.wpengine.com/?post_type=event&#038;p=1660", "0", "event", "", "0");
